	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Until recently, I had no idea that people were still making games for the great consoles/computers of yesteryear. I want in!
<br />
<br />Unfortunately, I have no programming knowledge whatsoever, only the desire to produce retro-styled video games. I have done some research on game development, but I'm still not sure just where to begin.
<br />
<br />That being said, I have a few questions for those in the know:
<br />
<br />-What console would be best to start out on?
<br />
<br />-What programming language should I learn first?
<br />
<br />-What tools will I need?
<br />
<br />-What do I really need to know to make a video game?
<br />
<br />Any information will be of much help, and greatly appreciated!

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


