		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">spikemtz wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">I have no programming knowledge whatsoever<br />[...]<br />-What console would be best to start out on?</div><br />PC.<br /><br /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">-What programming language should I learn first?</div><br />Python.<br /><br /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">-What tools will I need?</div><br />Python, Pygame, GIMP, and Audacity.<br /><br /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">-What do I really need to know to make a video game?</div>
<br />A basic understanding of <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Analytic_geometry" class="postlink">analytic geometry</a> helps immensely, as the concept of a pixel grid derives from it.

		

